    <item>
      <title>조진웅·박나래·조세호… 잇단 폭로·의혹에 방송가에도 불똥</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/09/2GZKNDYMVRE2ZLKIYRHTLJIDGU/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/09/2GZKNDYMVRE2ZLKIYRHTLJIDGU/</guid>
